1.0.name: wordpress/duster
1.0.description: Duster is a sophisticated theme designed and developed by Automattic, offering a unique page template to turn your blog into a showcase of different kinds of posts – Featured with an image, Asides, Link posts, and more. It also supports customization options like custom backgrounds, headers, menus, and widgets.
